item.description:
Join me for a  paddle around Pawtukaway lake. We can explore around the islands, stop to eat, swim or just hang. I don't have a time limit, just spend a nice day on the water. This event is open to all kayaks. Please bring and wear your pfd. Also cameras, water, lunch, sunscreen, bathing suit and maybe even a water toy. If you need a boat, one can be rented at the mountain Rd Trading post. It $35 for the whole day. They will supply everything you need. 603-895-3501.

Park admission is $4 pp. We will meet at the canoe launch.

So come join me on the water.

any questions..call me 603-315-0275

Rain will cancell this meetup.
